dct_description_sm: Norway. Oslo Oppmålingsvesen. Alternate title: Oppmålingsvesenets kart over Oslo (indre bydel). Bus routes and trams routes are indicated. Verso: street and plaza index, index of bus routes, parking laws in Oslo (English and Norwegian), insets: Trafikkart for Oslo with two enlargements of downtown Oslo; two maps showing distance by sea and land to other cities.
